                        |___/   Egress Governance

  Debian Bookworm | Clawgress MVPv1

  Operational mode:
    show agents          — list registered agents
    show audit           — view recent decisions
    show policies        — list policy rules
    show health          — system status
    configure            — enter configuration mode
    install              — install to disk

  Configuration mode (inside configure):
    set <path> <value>   — stage a change
    show                 — view candidate config
    commit               — apply changes
    discard              — discard candidate
    exit                 — return to operational mode

  Admin UI: http://localhost:8080/ui/
  Proxy:    localhost:3128

